Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:10.98,cn,,0,0,0,,1995年初 一名徒步旅行者在俄勒冈州中部偏远山区失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:18.00,cn,,0,0,0,,在几次目击之后 一些与世隔绝的当地社区成员开始猜测\N失踪男子感染了一种他们称之为"山热"的动物传播病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:21.30,cn,,0,0,0,,之前在这里生活的土著人称它为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:37.28,cn,,0,0,0,,玛伊冈·奥登瓦恩 或者"狼面人"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:10.79,cn,,0,0,0,,起床了\N{\ren}Ten-hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:38.81,cn,,0,0,0,,带上你的装备 我们七点出发\N{\ren}Grab your hunting pack. We're leaving at 0700.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.24,cn,,0,0,0,,这景色永不过时 对吧\N{\ren}This view never gets old, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.20,cn,,0,0,0,,百看不厌\N{\ren}No matter how many times you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.82,cn,,0,0,0,,啊 别靠近这些东西\N{\ren}Ah, don't go anywhere near those.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.99,cn,,0,0,0,,这些叫死亡帽蘑菇 这名字可不是开玩笑的\N{\ren}These are death cap mushrooms. The name ain't kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.45,cn,,0,0,0,,吃一个 你马上就进太平间\N{\ren}Eat one of those, you'll be wearing a toe tag real quick
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.48,cn,,0,0,0,,除非有人为你准备了一个全新的肝脏\N{\ren}unless someone's got a brand-new liver
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.31,cn,,0,0,0,,马上给你换上\N{\ren}lying around for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:09.21,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克 布莱克\N{\ren}Blake. Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.35,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克\N{\ren}Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.25,cn,,0,0,0,,你听到我说的了吗\N{\ren}Did you hear what I just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.32,cn,,0,0,0,,听到了\N{\ren}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:15.70,cn,,0,0,0,,我说了什么\N{\ren}What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.15,cn,,0,0,0,,别吃这些蘑菇\N{\ren}Don't eat the mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:18.57,cn,,0,0,0,,这些蘑菇叫什么\N{\ren}What are they called?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:21.47,cn,,0,0,0,,嗯…\N{\ren}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.47,cn,,0,0,0,,看吧 我就说你没听我讲话\N{\ren}See, this is what I'm talking about-- you're not hearing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.61,cn,,0,0,0,,你还活在你自己该死的世界里\N{\ren}You're off in your own goddamn world somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:28.82,cn,,0,0,0,,这个地方很美 但也很危险\N{\ren}This place is beautiful. It's also dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:32.48,cn,,0,0,0,,如果你知道该怎么做 你就能生存下去\N{\ren}You can survive if you know exactly what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.83,cn,,0,0,0,,是\N{\ren}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.90,cn,,0,0,0,,大家就是这样被夺走了…\N{\ren}People get taken from you-- like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:43.63,cn,,0,0,0,,死并不难\N{\ren}It's not hard to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:45.94,cn,,0,0,0,,这是世界上最简单的事\N{\ren}It's the easiest thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:48.94,cn,,0,0,0,,我们都\N{\ren}We are all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.46,cn,,0,0,0,,与它咫尺之遥\N{\ren}inches away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.85,cn,,0,0,0,,我没办法一直在你身边保护你\N{\ren}And I'm not always gonna be around to watch over you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.23,cn,,0,0,0,,但我会确保你清楚\N{\ren}but I'm gonna make damn sure that you know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.47,cn,,0,0,0,,如何生存下去 因为\N{\ren}how to survive as...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.33,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克\N{\ren}Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.34,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克\N{\ren}Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.87,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道你需要待在我身边的\N{\ren}You know you need to stay near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.19,cn,,0,0,0,,他妈的就待在我身边 小子\N{\ren}Right fucking next to me, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.19,cn,,0,0,0,,如果你不按我说的做 你会受伤的\N{\ren}If you don't do what I say, you get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.29,cn,,0,0,0,,你想受伤吗 想吗\N{\ren}Do you want to get hurt?! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.30,cn,,0,0,0,,你想受伤吗\N{\ren}Do you want to get hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.85,cn,,0,0,0,,不 我不想 只是\N{\ren}No, sir, I don't. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.27,cn,,0,0,0,,我只是想更容易打到鹿而已\N{\ren}I wanted to get a better shot at the deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.60,cn,,0,0,0,,到打鹿台去\N{\ren}Get up in that deer blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.19,cn,,0,0,0,,赶快\N{\ren}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.13,cn,,0,0,0,,捂住耳朵\N{\ren}Cover your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.16,cn,,0,0,0,,怎么了 爸爸\N{\ren}What was it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.69,cn,,0,0,0,,就一头熊\N{\ren}A bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.86,cn,,0,0,0,,山谷这边到处都是\N{\ren}They're all over this side of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.86,cn,,0,0,0,,稍作调整 我们走\N{\ren}Pick yourself up, and let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.97,cn,,0,0,0,,趁着天还有点光亮\N{\ren}while there's still some light left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.19,cn,,0,0,0,,基尔714 这里是洛威尔819\N{\ren}Kiel 714, this is Lovell 819.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.40,cn,,0,0,0,,基尔714 这里是洛威尔819\N{\ren}Kiel 714, this is Lovell 819.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:21.06,cn,,0,0,0,,基尔714 这里是洛威尔819 能听到吗\N{\ren}Kiel 714, this is Lovell 819. Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:25.75,cn,,0,0,0,,你到底在哪儿 丹\N{\ren}Where in the hell are you, Dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.96,cn,,0,0,0,,怎么了 格雷迪\N{\ren}DAN : What is it, Grady?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:30.97,cn,,0,0,0,,丹\N{\ren}Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.97,cn,,0,0,0,,我看到了\N{\ren}I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.45,cn,,0,0,0,,看到什么了\N{\ren}DAN: Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.77,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道我说的是什么\N{\ren}You know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.08,cn,,0,0,0,,那个徒步旅行的人吗\N{\ren}DAN: That hiker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.74,cn,,0,0,0,,狼面人吗\N{\ren}The face of the wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.09,cn,,0,0,0,,丹 那是真的\N{\ren}Dan, it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.26,cn,,0,0,0,,我在瞄准镜了看到它了\N{\ren}I had it in my scope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.06,cn,,0,0,0,,我差点就打中了\N{\ren}I almost shot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.27,cn,,0,0,0,,格雷迪 天黑以后\N{\ren}DAN: Grady, what is the point
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.99,cn,,0,0,0,,还上山找不并想\N{\ren}in going up that mountain after dark
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:00.75,cn,,0,0,0,,被发现的东西有什么意义吗\N{\ren}looking for something that doesn't want to be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:04.21,cn,,0,0,0,,我不是在找它\N{\ren}I wasn't looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:06.55,cn,,0,0,0,,我当时正在河边猎鹿\N{\ren}I was hunting deer down by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.25,cn,,0,0,0,,它在我儿子后面出现了\N{\ren}And it came after my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:11.59,cn,,0,0,0,,我会抓到它的 丹\N{\ren}I'm gonna get it, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:15.01,cn,,0,0,0,,你得跟我一起去\N{\ren}And you got to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.87,cn,,0,0,0,,难道你不想保证你儿子的安全吗\N{\ren}Don't you want to keep your boy safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.05,cn,,0,0,0,,我们能吃冰淇淋吗\N{\ren}Can we get some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:54.33,cn,,0,0,0,,可以吗 求你了 求你了 求你了\N{\ren}Please? Please, please, please, please, please, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.36,cn,,0,0,0,,我在博物馆给你买过热巧克力了\N{\ren}I got you a hot chocolate at the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.98,cn,,0,0,0,,那都不是甜点啊\N{\ren}That's not a dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.54,cn,,0,0,0,,那是饮料\N{\ren}That's a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.33,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 我觉得那算是甜点 大小姐\N{\ren}Oh, I think it's dessert, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:08.30,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道你是全世界最好的爸爸吗\N{\ren}Well, did you know you're the best dad in the whole world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.20,cn,,0,0,0,,知道啊 可是我敢肯定\N{\ren}Yeah, I'm sure the timing of that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.14,cn,,0,0,0,,这个跟冰淇淋没关系\N{\ren}has nothing to do with the ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.10,cn,,0,0,0,,是没有啊 我就是想告诉你\N{\ren}It doesn't. I just wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.73,cn,,0,0,0,,我很认真的\N{\ren}I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.83,cn,,0,0,0,,哎 怎么感觉像是场交易啊\N{\ren}Eh, this feels very transactional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:19.42,cn,,0,0,0,,我可不懂这是什么意思\N{\ren}I don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.32,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿 下来\N{\ren}Hey, get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.91,cn,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿\N{\ren}Ginger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.12,cn,,0,0,0,,马上给我下来\N{\ren}Get down right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.71,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧 你这样 就没冰淇淋吃了\N{\ren}Okay, that's it, no ice cream
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:32.43,cn,,0,0,0,,3 2 1\N{\ren}in three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.37,cn,,0,0,0,,狗他妈的就不会乱跑乱撞\N{\ren}No, the dog don't jump off the motherfucking leash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.33,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿\N{\ren}Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.86,cn,,0,0,0,,我跟你说了下来\N{\ren}I told you to get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.17,cn,,0,0,0,,为什么就不听我的话啊见鬼\N{\ren}Why didn't you listen to me, damn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:46.07,cn,,0,0,0,,为什么不听话\N{\ren}Why didn't you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.25,cn,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\ren}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.91,cn,,0,0,0,,对不起 我发脾气了\N{\ren}I'm sorry I lost my temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.25,cn,,0,0,0,,刚才那不是我\N{\ren}That's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.98,cn,,0,0,0,,我不想这样子\N{\ren}I don't want to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.91,cn,,0,0,0,,我只是需要你在我跟你讲事情的时候好好听着\N{\ren}I just need you to listen when I tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.99,cn,,0,0,0,,因为我的什么职责呢\N{\ren}'Cause what's my job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:10.26,cn,,0,0,0,,保证你女儿的安全\N{\ren}To keep your daughter safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.57,cn,,0,0,0,,对 是这样\N{\ren}Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.34,cn,,0,0,0,,那你的职责呢\N{\ren}And what's your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:15.86,cn,,0,0,0,,读心术\N{\ren}To read minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:20.79,cn,,0,0,0,,你能读出我现在在想什么吗\N{\ren}Can you guess what I'm thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.59,cn,,0,0,0,,"我爱我的小女儿"\N{\ren}"I love my little girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.73,cn,,0,0,0,,太厉害了吧\N{\ren}That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.11,cn,,0,0,0,,我就是这么想的\N{\ren}That's exactly what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.53,cn,,0,0,0,,你是怎么做到的\N{\ren}How do you do that every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.22,cn,,0,0,0,,你可太擅长了\N{\ren}You're so good at your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.39,cn,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.70,cn,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 你吓到我了 好吗\N{\ren}I'm sorry. You scared me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.26,cn,,0,0,0,,-你欠我一美元 -为什么啊\N{\ren}-You owe me a dollar. -Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.67,cn,,0,0,0,,因为你爆粗口了\N{\ren}Because you sweared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.09,cn,,0,0,0,,我没有 你幻听了\N{\ren}No, I didn't. You're hearing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.78,cn,,0,0,0,,没幻听 爸爸 你就是爆粗口了\N{\ren}I'm not, Daddy. You sweared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.58,cn,,0,0,0,,好了 我给你涂上吧\N{\ren}Okay, now let me put some on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.68,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 天呐 好吧 搞快点\N{\ren}Oh, my God. Okay, do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.07,cn,,0,0,0,,-真好看 -嗯哼 好看吗\N{\ren}-Beautiful. -Mm-hmm. Good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.62,cn,,0,0,0,,-好看啊 -怎么样\N{\ren}-Yeah. -How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.45,cn,,0,0,0,,你看起来好恐怖啊\N{\ren}You look creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.59,cn,,0,0,0,,你是说这样吗\N{\ren}You mean like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.32,cn,,0,0,0,,-你是说这样吗 宝贝儿 -爸爸\N{\ren}-You mean like this, Ginger? -Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.25,cn,,0,0,0,,不 额 好吧 不 我明白了\N{\ren}No, uh, yeah. No, I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.26,cn,,0,0,0,,好啦 坐到桌边去吧\N{\ren}Okay, go sit at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:16.50,cn,,0,0,0,,不 可是 我 我有第二个消息源的\N{\ren}No, but I-I have, I have a second source.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.61,cn,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\ren}One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.20,cn,,0,0,0,,那你是要把它报道出去\N{\ren}Well, are you gonna ship it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:24.41,cn,,0,0,0,,还是要让《泰晤士报》再挖我们的墙角呢\N{\ren}or you gonna let the Times scoop us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:26.13,cn,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 -嗨 妈咪\N{\ren}-Hi. -Hi, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.93,cn,,0,0,0,,那我们就这么说定了\N{\ren}Well, so we have a deal then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.07,cn,,0,0,0,,什么鬼 胡说八道\N{\ren}What-- This is bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.42,cn,,0,0,0,,你以前从未要求过这个\N{\ren}You've never asked for this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.01,cn,,0,0,0,,额 有处理这些破问题的时间\N{\ren}Uh, in the time it takes to do all of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.28,cn,,0,0,0,,我们本可以走在所有人前面的\N{\ren}we could've gotten ahead of everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.11,cn,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们没必要管那么多了\N{\ren}But I just don't think we need to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:46.15,cn,,0,0,0,,我保证可以现在就开始 你能上网吗\N{\ren}I promise from now on. Can you just get it online?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.36,cn,,0,0,0,,-去别的房间吧 -嘘\N{\ren}-Take that in the other room. -Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.88,cn,,0,0,0,,我本不该这么做的\N{\ren}I shouldn't be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.68,cn,,0,0,0,,你做还是不做\N{\ren}Are you doing it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:55.20,cn,,0,0,0,,夏洛特 你能去别的房间接吗\N{\ren}Charlotte, can you take that in the other room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:56.99,cn,,0,0,0,,听着 我 我知道自己在做什么\N{\ren}Listen, I-I know what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:00.17,cn,,0,0,0,,你清楚我是知道的 因为就是你教的我\N{\ren}You know I know because you taught me how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.86,cn,,0,0,0,,再见 夏洛特\N{\ren}Goodbye, Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.96,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧 再见\N{\ren}Okay. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.80,cn,,0,0,0,,你能 额\N{\ren}Can you, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:15.39,cn,,0,0,0,,你能不能不要这样\N{\ren}Can you not do that, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.22,cn,,0,0,0,,我怎么了\N{\ren}What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.22,cn,,0,0,0,,我刚才在跟我的编辑进行一次重要的谈话\N{\ren}I was having an important conversation with my editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.91,cn,,0,0,0,,对 因为只有你\N{\ren}Yeah, 'cause you're the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:23.26,cn,,0,0,0,,有重要的事情要做 是吧\N{\ren}that has important stuff going on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.23,cn,,0,0,0,,我都完全没事做的\N{\ren}I'm not busy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.85,cn,,0,0,0,,如果我有孩子 我绝不会在他们面前吵架\N{\ren}If I ever have kids, I'm never gonna fight in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.16,cn,,0,0,0,,我们没有吵架 亲爱的\N{\ren}We're not fighting, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.54,cn,,0,0,0,,我们正在进行热烈的交流\N{\ren}We're having a spirited exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.65,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.86,cn,,0,0,0,,所以 额\N{\ren}So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:45.21,cn,,0,0,0,,我刚刚得知我爸最终还是被宣布去世了\N{\ren}I just found out my dad has been finally declared deceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:49.28,cn,,0,0,0,,俄勒冈州的官方说法\N{\ren}Officially, by the state of Oregon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.77,cn,,0,0,0,,额 抱歉了\N{\ren}Um, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.33,cn,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\ren}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.37,cn,,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\N{\ren}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.88,cn,,0,0,0,,我是说 我们知道这封信总有一天会寄出的\N{\ren}I mean, we knew this letter was coming one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.51,cn,,0,0,0,,可是最后\N{\ren}But the finality of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.92,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊 我不知道 我还有些懵\N{\ren}Yeah, I don't know, it's still shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.93,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:13.76,cn,,0,0,0,,你很难过吗 爸爸\N{\ren}Are you sad, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.90,cn,,0,0,0,,我是难过的\N{\ren}I am, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.39,cn,,0,0,0,,我为很多事情感到难过\N{\ren}I'm sad about a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.60,cn,,0,0,0,,真希望我能更了解他一些\N{\ren}I wish I'd known him better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.22,cn,,0,0,0,,可他总是会让我害怕\N{\ren}But he always made me afraid of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:30.70,cn,,0,0,0,,所以我一长大就离开了\N{\ren}so as soon as I was old enough, I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.54,cn,,0,0,0,,我们很久没有聊过了\N{\ren}We hadn't spoken in a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.88,cn,,0,0,0,,因为我选择不说\N{\ren}because I chose not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:40.13,cn,,0,0,0,,额 而现在我再也不能和他讲话了\N{\ren}Um, and now that I can't speak to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.62,cn,,0,0,0,,我突然很想跟他聊聊\N{\ren}...I suddenly want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.14,cn,,0,0,0,,一整天\N{\ren}The whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:58.32,cn,,0,0,0,,不可能 整件事都很荒唐啊\N{\ren}No way. The whole thing felt ridiculous, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.29,cn,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\ren}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.40,cn,,0,0,0,,我待会儿去找你们\N{\ren}I'll catch up with you guys later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:07.91,cn,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.05,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\ren}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.51,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\ren}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.09,cn,,0,0,0,,惊喜啊\N{\ren}This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.61,cn,,0,0,0,,我给你带了午饭\N{\ren}I brought you some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.51,cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.62,cn,,0,0,0,,我们很久没有这个样子了\N{\ren}We haven't done this in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:24.76,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.98,cn,,0,0,0,,你开心吗 夏洛特\N{\ren}Are you happy, Charlotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.47,cn,,0,0,0,,开心啊\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.19,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.82,cn,,0,0,0,,那你呢\N{\ren}Are-are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.71,cn,,0,0,0,,为 为什么要这么问\N{\ren}Why-why are you asking me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.82,cn,,0,0,0,,因为我觉得我们做的并不好\N{\ren}Because I don't think we're doing well right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:03.00,cn,,0,0,0,,我来这里是因为\N{\ren}I came here because
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:06.25,cn,,0,0,0,,当我收到那封信的时候\N{\ren}when I got that letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:10.70,cn,,0,0,0,,我突然意识到\N{\ren}...it dawned on me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.88,cn,,0,0,0,,你跟宝贝儿是我唯一的亲人了\N{\ren}that you and Ginger are the only family that I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.44,cn,,0,0,0,,我们与人相处的时间是如此短暂\N{\ren}We have such a short amount of time with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:25.30,cn,,0,0,0,,我只希望我们都还在的时候\N{\ren}I just want us to enjoy each other
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:30.76,cn,,0,0,0,,能取悦彼此 努力让家庭幸福\N{\ren}and try to be happy as a family while we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.76,cn,,0,0,0,,我也想开心 可是\N{\ren}I want to be happy, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:46.53,cn,,0,0,0,,我在想 你应该跟我一起去俄勒冈\N{\ren}I was thinking you should come up to Oregon with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.81,cn,,0,0,0,,我得去一趟\N{\ren}I have to go up there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.19,cn,,0,0,0,,把我爸的东西都打包装车\N{\ren}and pack up all my dad's stuff in a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.88,cn,,0,0,0,,咱们为什么不一起去呢\N{\ren}Why don't we all go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:19:59.68,cn,,0,0,0,,我们可以在那儿一起过整个夏天\N{\ren}We'd spend the whole summer up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:01.75,cn,,0,0,0,,我感觉对我们是件好事\N{\ren}I think it'd be good for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.72,cn,,0,0,0,,那个地方相当让人惊叹\N{\ren}It really is stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:13.18,cn,,0,0,0,,离农场不远有个山谷\N{\ren}There's this valley not far from the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.73,cn,,0,0,0,,就在这两座山之间\N{\ren}It's between these mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:20.08,cn,,0,0,0,,无论你看多少次 那景色都会\N{\ren}And no matter how many times you see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:24.40,cn,,0,0,0,,让你觉得一切会好起来的\N{\ren}the view makes you feel like everything's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.40,cn,,0,0,0,,我想让你跟宝贝儿去看看\N{\ren}I want you and Ginger to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.95,cn,,0,0,0,,听起来不错啊 可我工作走不开啊\N{\ren}It sounds nice, but I can't just leave work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.13,cn,,0,0,0,,是 不过你可以远程工作啊\N{\ren}No, yeah, but you can work remotely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.79,cn,,0,0,0,,休息一段时间吧\N{\ren}Just take some time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.03,cn,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿会很开心的\N{\ren}Ginger would love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.17,cn,,0,0,0,,你可以花点时间陪陪她\N{\ren}You could spend some time with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:39.45,cn,,0,0,0,,你也能写你的书了\N{\ren}You can work on your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:42.93,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊 我不\N{\ren}Yeah, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.80,cn,,0,0,0,,我甚至都不知道自己还擅不擅长了\N{\ren}I don't even know if I'm good at that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.59,cn,,0,0,0,,你是个好作家呀\N{\ren}You're a great writer. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:54.11,cn,,0,0,0,,我是说陪女儿\N{\ren}I meant at spending time with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.36,cn,,0,0,0,,她\N{\ren}She...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.78,cn,,0,0,0,,相比于我 她跟你更亲近\N{\ren}She relates to you so much more than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.72,cn,,0,0,0,,你是一位了不起的母亲\N{\ren}You are an incredible mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.24,cn,,0,0,0,,你是的 馁\N{\ren}You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:22.76,cn,,0,0,0,,跟我去吧\N{\ren}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:53.07,cn,,0,0,0,,好了 好了 我想到一个\N{\ren}Okay, okay, I've got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:55.87,cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 你是住在水里吗\N{\ren}Mm, do you live in water?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:57.45,cn,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\ren}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:21:58.66,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:02.32,cn,,0,0,0,,你住在森林里吗\N{\ren}Do you live in the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.32,cn,,0,0,0,,有时候吧\N{\ren}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:06.22,cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 你会飞吗\N{\ren}Mm, can you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:08.02,cn,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\ren}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:10.50,cn,,0,0,0,,你是用四条腿走路吗\N{\ren}Do you walk on four legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:11.74,cn,,0,0,0,,-是啊 -是吗\N{\ren}-Yes. -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:13.19,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 你是头鹿吗\N{\ren}Oh, are you a deer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:14.71,cn,,0,0,0,,额 不是\N{\ren}Uh... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.89,cn,,0,0,0,,额 那你是头熊吗\N{\ren}Uh, are you a bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:18.20,cn,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.34,0:22:19.75,cn,,0,0,0,,是狗吗\N{\ren}Are you a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:21.20,cn,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.17,cn,,0,0,0,,不 我只是不知道\N{\ren}No. I just don't know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:23.72,cn,,0,0,0,,不知道答案\N{\ren}Don't know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:25.97,cn,,0,0,0,,-不 我是头麑 -麑吗\N{\ren}-No, I'm a fawn. -A fawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:27.52,cn,,0,0,0,,-对 -我说过鹿了呀\N{\ren}-Yeah. -I said deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.69,cn,,0,0,0,,-麑不是鹿 -是\N{\ren}-A fawn is not a deer. -It's-it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:31.94,cn,,0,0,0,,-不是的 -什么啊 就是鹿的小时候啊\N{\ren}-It's not. -What? It's literally a baby deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:33.35,cn,,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\ren}It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:34.42,cn,,0,0,0,,魔生活在森林里 好不好\N{\ren}And fawns live in the forest. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:35.77,cn,,0,0,0,,它们有时在森林里 但有时\N{\ren}They do sometimes, but sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:37.39,cn,,0,0,0,,它们会出现在人们的后院 所以\N{\ren}they're in people's backyards, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:38.77,cn,,0,0,0,,-哦 哦 -什么 那是\N{\ren}-Oh. Oh. -What? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:40.57,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 你骗人 你知道吗\N{\ren}Oh, you are a cheater. You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:42.08,cn,,0,0,0,,-这样吧 你知道我要干什么吗 -别 爸爸 住手\N{\ren}-That's it. You know what's coming? -Don't, Daddy. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:43.47,cn,,0,0,0,,-爸爸 停下来 不要啊 妈咪 -喔呼 喔呼\N{\ren}-Daddy, stop. No, Mommy. -Uh-oh. Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.12,cn,,0,0,0,,-跟爸爸说让他成熟点啊 -喔呼\N{\ren}-Tell Daddy he's being immature. -Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:48.16,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 我是可以跟他一样不成熟哟\N{\ren}Hey, hey, I can be just as immature as he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.78,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪 不要啊 停下来啊 妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy, stop it. Stop, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:51.40,cn,,0,0,0,,你凭什么觉得我很成熟啊\N{\ren}What makes you think I'm so mature?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:53.06,cn,,0,0,0,,-啊 啊 -不要啊 妈咪 停下来\N{\ren}-Huh? Huh? -Stop it, Mommy. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:54.44,cn,,0,0,0,,求你了妈咪 别闹啦\N{\ren}Please, Mommy, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:56.62,cn,,0,0,0,,-妈咪 不要啦 -求我\N{\ren}-Mommy, stop it. -Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:58.07,cn,,0,0,0,,求你啦 妈咪 别闹啦\N{\ren}Please, Mommy, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:03.59,cn,,0,0,0,,等等 这就是吗 该死\N{\ren}Wait, is this it? Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:06.11,cn,,0,0,0,,-爸爸 -抱歉 亲爱的 我的错\N{\ren}-Dad. -Sorry, honey. Shivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:10.94,cn,,0,0,0,,我看下地图\N{\ren}Let me check the map here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:16.26,cn,,0,0,0,,我手机没有信号\N{\ren}I have no service.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:18.26,cn,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\ren}Me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:24.92,cn,,0,0,0,,不过这里看起来确实很眼熟\N{\ren}This does look familiar, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:30.27,cn,,0,0,0,,我可以看看吗\N{\ren}Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.62,cn,,0,0,0,,树屋里有人\N{\ren}There's someone in that tree house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:36.00,cn,,0,0,0,,哪里\N{\ren}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:37.14,cn,,0,0,0,,那边\N{\ren}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:39.94,cn,,0,0,0,,她说得对 那东西里面有人\N{\ren}She's right-- there's someone inside that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:44.73,cn,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\ren}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:52.67,cn,,0,0,0,,额 我们走吧 布莱克\N{\ren}Uh, let's go, Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.81,0:23:53.88,cn,,0,0,0,,不 没关系的\N{\ren}No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:55.78,cn,,0,0,0,,不行啊 他有枪\N{\ren}No, he has a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:23:57.78,cn,,0,0,0,,夏洛特 这里每个人都有枪的\N{\ren}Charlotte, everyone around here has a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:23:59.82,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克 咱能开车走人吗\N{\ren}Blake, can-can you just please drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.41,cn,,0,0,0,,-晚上好 -嘿\N{\ren}-MAN: Evening. -Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:08.48,cn,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪儿啊\N{\ren}Where you guys headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.62,0:24:10.73,cn,,0,0,0,,额 我在找我爸的农场\N{\ren}Uh, I'm looking for my dad's farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:13.87,cn,,0,0,0,,我只是有段时间没来了 忘记怎么走\N{\ren}I just, I haven't been up here in a while. I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:15.32,cn,,0,0,0,,你爸是谁\N{\ren}Who's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.45,0:24:17.18,cn,,0,0,0,,额 格雷迪\N{\ren}Uh... Grady.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:19.91,cn,,0,0,0,,洛威尔\N{\ren}Lovell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.49,0:24:23.91,cn,,0,0,0,,你可是离开很久了 布雷克\N{\ren}You've been gone a long time, Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.19,cn,,0,0,0,,等等 我 我认识你吗\N{\ren}Wait, do I... do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.88,0:24:30.78,cn,,0,0,0,,我是德里克 我是丹·基尔的儿子\N{\ren}I'm Derek. I'm Dan Kiel's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.16,0:24:33.64,cn,,0,0,0,,是哦\N{\ren}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.78,0:24:35.65,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 德里克 见鬼\N{\ren}Oh, Derek. Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:37.72,cn,,0,0,0,,-爸爸 -哦 不好意思\N{\ren}-Dad. -Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.86,0:24:39.44,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊 我记得你\N{\ren}Yeah, no, I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.58,0:24:41.55,cn,,0,0,0,,你好吗 很高兴见到你\N{\ren}How are you? It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.21,0:24:44.90,cn,,0,0,0,,住在这里的人已经不多了\N{\ren}Not many of us left living up here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.21,0:24:47.93,cn,,0,0,0,,都不算是整个世界的一部分了\N{\ren}Not really a part of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.07,0:24:50.04,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊 我再同意不过了\N{\ren}Yeah. I-I'd agree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.80,0:24:55.05,cn,,0,0,0,,你可能不记得了 但是 额一般来说\N{\ren}You might not remember this, but, uh, for the most part,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.18,0:24:57.19,cn,,0,0,0,,我们不喜欢天黑后上山的\N{\ren}we don't like to be out after dark on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.32,0:24:58.74,cn,,0,0,0,,这里没有电 没有灯\N{\ren}There's no power grid, no lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.88,0:25:01.43,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 我还以为只是我爸这样\N{\ren}Oh. I-I thought that was just my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.57,0:25:04.23,cn,,0,0,0,,额 你知道 我其实有点迷路了\N{\ren}Uh, you know, I'm actually a little lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.36,0:25:07.16,cn,,0,0,0,,我确定这是他的车道\N{\ren}You know, I-I was sure that this was his driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.09,0:25:09.54,cn,,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\ren}It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.79,0:25:11.99,cn,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\ren}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.13,0:25:13.68,cn,,0,0,0,,这是我的\N{\ren}It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.07,0:25:16.20,cn,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\ren}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.72,0:25:19.07,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\ren}Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.21,0:25:20.66,cn,,0,0,0,,抱歉了\N{\ren}Well, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.80,0:25:23.52,cn,,0,0,0,,通往格雷迪家的那条老路被切断了\N{\ren}The usual road to Grady's is cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.66,0:25:26.25,cn,,0,0,0,,我带你过去吧 让你快点安顿下来\N{\ren}I'll take you there, get you settled in quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.66,0:25:29.60,cn,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.36,0:25:33.26,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克 不 绝对不行\N{\ren}Blake, no. No, absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.39,0:25:34.74,cn,,0,0,0,,-没关系的 让他给咱带路 -不 他\N{\ren}-It's fine. Let him show us. -No, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.88,0:25:36.57,cn,,0,0,0,,为什么他不能告诉我们怎么走呢\N{\ren}Why can't he just tell us where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.71,0:25:38.26,cn,,0,0,0,,-他现在就在这儿了 -什么 那\N{\ren}-He's standing there now. -What, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.40,0:25:39.54,cn,,0,0,0,,-开门吧 小夏 -你在说什么\N{\ren}-Just open the door, Char. -What are you talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.68,0:25:40.88,cn,,0,0,0,,-他已经在开了 -别\N{\ren}-He's opening it. -Well, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.02,0:25:42.54,cn,,0,0,0,,嗨 嗨\N{\ren}Hi. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.61,0:25:46.41,cn,,0,0,0,,嗨 额 不 不 不\N{\ren}Hi. Uh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.55,0:25:48.93,cn,,0,0,0,,没关系 我坐到后面去吧\N{\ren}It's okay. I-I'll just go to the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.76,0:25:53.41,cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢 女士\N{\ren}Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.83,0:25:56.76,cn,,0,0,0,,看好脚\N{\ren}Watch your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.87,0:26:03.49,cn,,0,0,0,,往前走一段路就到了\N{\ren}Just go straight on a ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.74,0:26:06.63,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿 小可爱\N{\ren}Hey there, cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.77,0:26:09.46,cn,,0,0,0,,额 德雷克 这是我女儿和我妻子夏洛特\N{\ren}Uh, Derek, that's Ginger and my wife Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.60,0:26:10.95,cn,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\ren}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.24,0:26:31.56,cn,,0,0,0,,你们打算待多久\N{\ren}How long you planning on staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.69,0:26:34.01,cn,,0,0,0,,-待不长 -就一阵子\N{\ren}-Not too long. -A little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.05,0:26:43.84,cn,,0,0,0,,这绝对是一种后天养成的味道\N{\ren}It's definitely an acquired taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.84,0:26:48.19,cn,,0,0,0,,在这里 有些事你不得不去接受\N{\ren}There are things you have to come to terms with up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.50,0:26:51.09,cn,,0,0,0,,动物\N{\ren}Animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.09,0:26:53.65,cn,,0,0,0,,疾病\N{\ren}Diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.99,0:26:58.89,cn,,0,0,0,,我们都是很坚强的人\N{\ren}Well, we're, we're pretty tough people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.48,0:27:03.52,cn,,0,0,0,,是这样吗\N{\ren}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.11,0:27:07.76,cn,,0,0,0,,在我看来 你们并不坚强\N{\ren}To me, you don't seem so tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.15,0:27:12.29,cn,,0,0,0,,这是件好事情\N{\ren}That's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.42,0:27:14.84,cn,,0,0,0,,说明你们过得不错\N{\ren}Means you got a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.98,0:27:17.53,cn,,0,0,0,,你们健康 安全\N{\ren}You're healthy, safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.16,0:27:25.30,cn,,0,0,0,,你爸的家就在前面\N{\ren}Your dad's place is just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.96,0:27:29.03,cn,,0,0,0,,你是做什么工作的 布雷克\N{\ren}What do you do for a living, Blake?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.16,0:27:30.68,cn,,0,0,0,,我是个作家\N{\ren}I'm a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.82,0:27:32.72,cn,,0,0,0,,不过现在正处于工作间隙\N{\ren}I'm between jobs right now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.48,0:27:38.07,cn,,0,0,0,,所以 我是后面\N{\ren}So... I'm a dad
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.21,0:27:40.21,cn,,0,0,0,,那个小怪物的全职爸爸\N{\ren}to that monster in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.56,0:27:49.15,cn,,0,0,0,,我是个记者\N{\ren}I'm a journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.34,0:28:07.62,cn,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌 你每天看着她们都会想 你怎么会这么幸运\N{\ren}I bet you look at them every day and wonder how you got so lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.76,0:28:09.93,cn,,0,0,0,,拥有如此聪慧美丽的一家人\N{\ren}to have such a smart and beautiful family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.79,0:28:14.49,cn,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\ren}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.63,0:28:17.83,cn,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\ren}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.86,0:28:42.20,cn,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\ren}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.41,0:28:45.38,cn,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\ren}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.52,0:28:47.42,cn,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿 你还好吗\N{\ren}Ginger? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.55,0:28:48.52,cn,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\ren}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.66,0:28:50.90,cn,,0,0,0,,小夏 你呢\N{\ren}Char, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.04,0:28:52.49,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿 你伤到哪儿了吗\N{\ren}Hey, are you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.63,0:28:55.15,cn,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 宝贝儿\N{\ren}Are you okay? Ginger?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.29,0:28:56.67,cn,,0,0,0,,夏洛特 你受伤了吗\N{\ren}Charlotte, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.80,0:28:58.56,cn,,0,0,0,,-没有 -咦\N{\ren}-No. -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.63,0:29:00.88,cn,,0,0,0,,德雷克 你还好吗\N{\ren}Derek, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.02,0:29:02.46,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 不 不 不 不\N{\ren}Hey, hey, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.67,0:29:06.61,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 见鬼\N{\ren}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.75,0:29:09.30,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们得离开这里\N{\ren}Okay. We got to get out of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.44,0:29:10.82,cn,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿 宝贝儿\N{\ren}Ginger. Ginger.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.96,0:29:12.16,cn,,0,0,0,,-不 不 不 -宝贝儿 看着我\N{\ren}-No, no, no. -Ginger, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.30,0:29:13.79,cn,,0,0,0,,不 拜托 拜托不\N{\ren}No, please. Please, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.92,0:29:14.65,cn,,0,0,0,,你得从窗户爬出去\N{\ren}You got to climb through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.79,0:29:16.27,cn,,0,0,0,,看着我 宝贝儿\N{\ren}Look at me, Ginger.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.41,0:29:18.00,cn,,0,0,0,,从窗户爬出去 你能做到的 亲爱的\N{\ren}Climb through the window. You can do it, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.14,0:29:19.93,cn,,0,0,0,,不行 爸爸 我怕我会掉下去\N{\ren}No, Daddy, I'm scared I'm gonna fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.07,0:29:21.66,cn,,0,0,0,,-你不会有事的 你没事的 -我会掉下去的\N{\ren}-You'll be okay. You'll be okay. -I'm gonna fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.79,0:29:23.21,cn,,0,0,0,,我会掉下去的 我会掉下去的\N{\ren}I'm gonna fall. I'm gonna fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.35,0:29:24.87,cn,,0,0,0,,没事的 爬到上面去\N{\ren}It's okay. Just get onto the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.00,0:29:26.80,cn,,0,0,0,,就待在那儿\N{\ren}Just stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.94,0:29:28.63,cn,,0,0,0,,就坐那儿 亲爱的\N{\ren}Just sit right there, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.56,0:29:34.43,cn,,0,0,0,,待在那儿别动 亲爱的 妈咪这就来\N{\ren}Just stay there, honey. Mommy's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.05,0:29:37.81,cn,,0,0,0,,夏洛特 上\N{\ren}Charlotte, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.95,0:29:43.26,cn,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\ren}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.33,0:29:46.09,cn,,0,0,0,,待在那儿 我这就来\N{\ren}Stay right there. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.23,0:29:48.41,cn,,0,0,0,,我\N{\ren}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.83,0:31:06.38,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.52,0:31:08.59,cn,,0,0,0,,我们得下去 在这儿等着\N{\ren}We got to get down. Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.22,0:31:13.60,cn,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\ren}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.73,0:31:14.87,cn,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿 亲爱的 你得跳了\N{\ren}Ginger, honey, you have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.01,0:31:16.39,cn,,0,0,0,,来吧 我会接住你的\N{\ren}Come on. I'm gonna catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.91,0:31:20.15,cn,,0,0,0,,好了 夏洛特 来吧\N{\ren}Okay. All right, Charlotte, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.54,0:31:23.64,cn,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\ren}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.78,0:31:24.71,cn,,0,0,0,,-没事 没事 -没事吗\N{\ren}-No, yeah. Yeah. Yeah. -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.85,0:31:26.09,cn,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿 你受伤了吗\N{\ren}Ginger, are you hurt at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.23,0:31:27.61,cn,,0,0,0,,-没有 -好的 来吧\N{\ren}-No. -Okay, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.75,0:31:28.65,cn,,0,0,0,,我们得走了 我们必须找到房子\N{\ren}We got to go. We have to find the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.78,0:31:30.06,cn,,0,0,0,,看好脚下 来 亲爱的\N{\ren}Watch your step. Come on, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.20,0:31:31.10,cn,,0,0,0,,我们得加快脚步了\N{\ren}We got to move quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.23,0:31:33.58,cn,,0,0,0,,那里安全些 来\N{\ren}Where it's safer. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.72,0:31:36.03,cn,,0,0,0,,小心 亲爱的 小心 小心\N{\ren}Careful, honey. Careful, careful, careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.17,0:31:38.55,cn,,0,0,0,,-爸爸 我累了 -什么\N{\ren}-Daddy, I'm tired. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.69,0:31:39.93,cn,,0,0,0,,-我走不动了 -好吧\N{\ren}-I can't go. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.90,0:31:43.38,cn,,0,0,0,,夏洛特\N{\ren}Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.52,0:31:44.90,cn,,0,0,0,,好的 亲爱的\N{\ren}Okay, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.73,0:31:48.35,cn,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\ren}Quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.70,0:31:52.05,cn,,0,0,0,,来吧 我记得这里\N{\ren}Come on, I recognize this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.19,0:31:53.57,cn,,0,0,0,,很近了\N{\ren}We're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.70,0:31:55.05,cn,,0,0,0,,我把你放在这儿 亲爱的 好吗\N{\ren}I'm gonna put you down here, honey, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.19,0:31:57.12,cn,,0,0,0,,-好把 -手给我\N{\ren}-Okay. -Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.26,0:31:58.36,cn,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\ren}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.50,0:31:59.50,cn,,0,0,0,,-来 -小心\N{\ren}-Come on. -Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.64,0:32:01.30,cn,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\ren}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.89,0:32:04.75,cn,,0,0,0,,来 来\N{\ren}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.89,0:32:06.65,cn,,0,0,0,,就是这里\N{\ren}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.27,0:32:10.00,cn,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\ren}Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.14,0:32:12.41,cn,,0,0,0,,跑啊 亲爱的\N{\ren}Run, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.55,0:32:14.07,cn,,0,0,0,,来啊 亲爱的\N{\ren}Go, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.24,0:32:16.45,cn,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\ren}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.59,0:32:18.28,cn,,0,0,0,,快 快\N{\ren}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.42,0:32:20.08,cn,,0,0,0,,来\N{\ren}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.81,0:32:27.26,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快点\N{\ren}Daddy, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.39,0:32:28.77,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快啊\N{\ren}Daddy, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.91,0:32:30.16,cn,,0,0,0,,赶紧 进屋\N{\ren}Come on. Get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.28,0:32:48.97,cn,,0,0,0,,等等 等等\N{\ren}Wait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.70,0:33:00.05,cn,,0,0,0,,-待在这儿 -爸爸 你要去哪儿啊\N{\ren}-Stay right here. -Daddy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.19,0:33:01.43,cn,,0,0,0,,-我马上回来 -爸爸 爸爸\N{\ren}-I'll be right back. -Daddy. Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.57,0:33:02.81,cn,,0,0,0,,-跟妈咪待在一起 -爸爸\N{\ren}-Stay with Mommy. -Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.47,0:33:45.75,cn,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.91,0:34:44.46,cn,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\ren}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.21,0:35:10.83,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\ren}Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.97,0:35:12.14,cn,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\ren}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.11,0:35:17.84,cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 没事了\N{\ren}Mm. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.98,0:35:19.43,cn,,0,0,0,,我们安全了\N{\ren}We're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.19,0:35:25.85,cn,,0,0,0,,我想回家\N{\ren}I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.16,0:35:29.47,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\ren}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.61,0:35:30.85,cn,,0,0,0,,会回去的\N{\ren}We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.96,0:35:34.17,cn,,0,0,0,,我们现在还不能出去 躺下吧\N{\ren}We just can't go outside right now. Lay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.51,0:35:38.03,cn,,0,0,0,,我们只能等到明天早上了\N{\ren}We just have to wait until the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.17,0:35:39.79,cn,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\ren}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.91,0:36:28.19,cn,,0,0,0,,不 哪儿也不要去\N{\ren}No, don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.57,0:36:31.53,cn,,0,0,0,,好的 好的 我就在这儿\N{\ren}Okay, okay. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.88,0:36:34.23,cn,,0,0,0,,我哪儿也不去\N{\ren}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.36,0:36:36.88,cn,,0,0,0,,我在这儿 就在这儿\N{\ren}I'm gonna be right here. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.85,0:36:42.72,cn,,0,0,0,,那个人死了吗\N{\ren}Is that man dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.03,0:36:46.20,cn,,0,0,0,,从树屋出来的那个人\N{\ren}The man who came out the tree house?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.52,0:36:50.17,cn,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\ren}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.91,0:36:59.98,cn,,0,0,0,,大概率他死了\N{\ren}Most likely, he did die.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.43,0:37:03.57,cn,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉让你发生了这样的事\N{\ren}I'm so sorry that this happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.71,0:37:10.75,cn,,0,0,0,,保护你是我的职责\N{\ren}It's my job to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.88,0:37:12.75,cn,,0,0,0,,我却没有做到\N{\ren}And I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.96,0:37:17.41,cn,,0,0,0,,我让你经历了一件非常可怕的事情\N{\ren}I've put you through something very scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.72,0:37:24.45,cn,,0,0,0,,如果这件事一直这样困扰着你\N{\ren}And I'd never be able to forgive myself
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.59,0:37:26.49,cn,,0,0,0,,我永远都无法原谅我自己\N{\ren}if this stayed with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.28,0:37:30.28,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 如果这件事给你留下了伤痕\N{\ren}You know? If it scarred you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.91,0:37:36.50,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 当你是一个父亲\N{\ren}You know, sometimes when you're a daddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.63,0:37:38.19,cn,,0,0,0,,你会很害怕你的孩子留下伤痕的\N{\ren}you're so scared of your kids getting scars,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.33,0:37:40.47,cn,,0,0,0,,因为你就会成为给他们留下伤疤的那个人\N{\ren}you become the thing that scars 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.79,0:37:58.48,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿 我现在在想什么\N{\ren}Hey, what am I thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.01,0:38:08.94,cn,,0,0,0,,"我爱我的小女儿"\N{\ren}"I love my little girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.53,0:38:11.98,cn,,0,0,0,,太不可思议了\N{\ren}That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.33,0:38:14.78,cn,,0,0,0,,你一定会读心术\N{\ren}You must be able to read minds,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.91,0:38:18.09,cn,,0,0,0,,因为我就是在想这个\N{\ren}because that's exactly what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.95,0:38:22.30,cn,,0,0,0,,一字不差\N{\ren}Word for word.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.75,0:38:25.13,cn,,0,0,0,,好啦\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.99,0:38:27.37,cn,,0,0,0,,爱你\N{\ren}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.51,0:38:28.86,cn,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿\N{\ren}I'll be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.00,0:38:30.72,cn,,0,0,0,,记住 这是我的职责\N{\ren}Remember, that's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.86,0:38:33.03,cn,,0,0,0,,我不会让你出任何事的\N{\ren}I'm not gonna let anything happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.69,0:38:39.42,cn,,0,0,0,,我想我们应该 额\N{\ren}I think we should, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.56,0:38:41.25,cn,,0,0,0,,我想我们应该把前门挡上\N{\ren}I think we should cover the front door,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.39,0:38:43.70,cn,,0,0,0,,因为如果那东西 如果它一直想进来\N{\ren}'cause if that thing... if it keeps trying to get in,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.84,0:38:45.50,cn,,0,0,0,,门上的铰链会脱落的\N{\ren}the whole door can come off the hinges.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.46,0:38:48.05,cn,,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么东西\N{\ren}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.19,0:38:49.81,cn,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\ren}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.95,0:38:52.33,cn,,0,0,0,,那他妈是什么鬼东西 布雷克\N{\ren}What the fuck was that thing, Blake?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.37,0:38:54.68,cn,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\ren}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.47,0:38:57.85,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道听起来像动物\N{\ren}I know it sounded like an animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.99,0:39:02.82,cn,,0,0,0,,可当我们差点撞到它的时候 我直直地看着它\N{\ren}but I looked right at it when we almost hit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.20,0:39:08.62,cn,,0,0,0,,我发誓 它是用两只脚站起来的\N{\ren}and I swear to God it was standing up on two feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.76,0:39:10.11,cn,,0,0,0,,就像个人\N{\ren}like a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.37,0:39:30.44,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克\N{\ren}Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.24,0:39:40.93,cn,,0,0,0,,能撑得住吗\N{\ren}Is that gonna hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.73,0:39:47.18,cn,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\ren}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.08,0:39:55.60,cn,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该试着打电话求救\N{\ren}I think we should try to call somebody for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.02,0:39:59.36,cn,,0,0,0,,怎么打\N{\ren}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.06,0:40:13.13,cn,,0,0,0,,喂 测试\N{\ren}Hello? Test.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.00,0:40:16.90,cn,,0,0,0,,喂 这里是洛威尔 819\N{\ren}Hello. This is Lovell 819.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.04,0:40:18.31,cn,,0,0,0,,有人能听到吗\N{\ren}Can anyone hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.28,0:40:20.66,cn,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\ren}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.80,0:40:22.56,cn,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\ren}Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.91,0:40:34.12,cn,,0,0,0,,天呐 这是什么味道\N{\ren}Jesus, what is that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.26,0:40:36.43,cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 什么 你说什么\N{\ren}Hmm? What? What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.36,0:41:04.46,cn,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\ren}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.29,0:41:06.88,cn,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\ren}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.99,0:41:19.86,cn,,0,0,0,,我找到吃的了\N{\ren}Well, I found something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.99,0:41:21.31,cn,,0,0,0,,我爸做的牛肉干\N{\ren}My dad's jerky.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.80,0:41:31.39,cn,,0,0,0,,我的下巴 一定是撞到方向盘了\N{\ren}My jaw. I must've hit it on the steering wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.74,0:41:44.54,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 该死\N{\ren}Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.06,0:41:57.65,cn,,0,0,0,,给你 给\N{\ren}Here. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.97,0:42:04.07,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐\N{\ren}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.21,0:42:05.94,cn,,0,0,0,,好了 来坐下\N{\ren}Okay. Come on. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.08,0:42:08.11,cn,,0,0,0,,坐好 没事的\N{\ren}Just sit. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.25,0:42:10.70,cn,,0,0,0,,抬胳膊\N{\ren}Just lift your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.67,0:42:18.29,cn,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\ren}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.23,0:42:26.75,cn,,0,0,0,,我想是被卡车的窗户割伤的\N{\ren}I think I cut it on the window in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.89,0:42:28.37,cn,,0,0,0,,我不 我不知道\N{\ren}I-I don't... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.51,0:42:31.72,cn,,0,0,0,,看起来你不像是被玻璃割伤的\N{\ren}This doesn't look like you got cut by glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.59,0:42:36.38,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧 额\N{\ren}Okay. Okay. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.25,0:42:40.77,cn,,0,0,0,,抬起胳膊\N{\ren}Lift your arm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.90,0:42:43.04,cn,,0,0,0,,好了 我试一试\N{\ren}All right, j-just try a little bit. Just try.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.66,0:43:11.52,cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.42,0:43:14.90,cn,,0,0,0,,继续帮我试CB无线电\N{\ren}Keep trying the CB radio for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.28,0:43:17.63,cn,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\ren}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.20,0:43:40.48,cn,,0,0,0,,天呐 宝贝儿\N{\ren}Jesus, Ginger.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.62,0:43:42.24,cn,,0,0,0,,对不起 我吵醒你了 亲爱的\N{\ren}I'm sorry I woke you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.38,0:43:44.14,cn,,0,0,0,,睡觉去吧 好吗 你需要休息一下\N{\ren}Just go back to bed, okay? You need to get your rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.86,0:43:47.00,cn,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿\N{\ren}Ginger.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.21,0:43:49.63,cn,,0,0,0,,听话 好吗\N{\ren}Will you listen to me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.77,0:43:52.22,cn,,0,0,0,,回床上去 快半夜了\N{\ren}Go back to bed. It's almost midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.15,0:43:57.60,cn,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\ren}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.84,0:44:02.64,cn,,0,0,0,,你联系到CB上的什么人了吗\N{\ren}Did you reach anyone on the CB?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.06,0:44:11.34,cn,,0,0,0,,我 我没\N{\ren}I-I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.51,0:44:15.86,cn,,0,0,0,,我马上就好\N{\ren}I'll be done in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.24,0:44:23.32,cn,,0,0,0,,真诡异啊\N{\ren}How odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.71,0:45:10.43,cn,,0,0,0,,喔\N{\ren}Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.74,0:49:16.64,cn,,0,0,0,,嘘\N{\ren}Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.15,0:50:19.98,cn,,0,0,0,,- 夏洛特 -布莱克 布莱克\N{\ren}-Charlotte. -Blake. Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.19,0:50:25.61,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克\N{\ren}Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.20,0:50:28.72,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.85,0:50:30.23,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.37,0:50:32.72,cn,,0,0,0,,-回去 回去 -妈咪 妈咪\N{\ren}-Get back! Get back! -Mommy. Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.86,0:50:34.45,cn,,0,0,0,,回去\N{\ren}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.93,0:50:40.04,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克 布莱克\N{\ren}Blake. Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.38,0:51:52.07,cn,,0,0,0,,小夏\N{\ren}Char?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.82,0:52:45.68,cn,,0,0,0,,能听到吗\N{\ren}Can you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.82,0:52:53.69,cn,,0,0,0,,有谁能听到吗\N{\ren}Can anybody hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.76,0:52:56.66,cn,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\ren}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.01,0:53:03.56,cn,,0,0,0,,有谁能听到吗\N{\ren}Can anybody hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.70,0:53:05.94,cn,,0,0,0,,这里是夏洛特·洛威尔\N{\ren}This is Charlotte Lovell.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.08,0:53:09.15,cn,,0,0,0,,如果有人能听到我的声音 请回复\N{\ren}If someone can hear me, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.29,0:53:12.09,cn,,0,0,0,,我丈夫病了\N{\ren}My-my husband is, uh, sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.22,0:53:16.78,cn,,0,0,0,,如果有人能听到的话\N{\ren}Um, if-if anyone can, uh, can hear me, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.92,0:53:19.89,cn,,0,0,0,,请找人来帮忙\N{\ren}pl-please call someone to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.02,0:53:23.20,cn,,0,0,0,,我们遭到了某种动物的攻击\N{\ren}We were attacked by some kind of animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.34,0:53:28.93,cn,,0,0,0,,我觉得我丈夫也被感染了\N{\ren}and I-I think my, um, husband was infected by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.38,0:53:32.97,cn,,0,0,0,,他\N{\ren}He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.11,0:53:35.14,cn,,0,0,0,,他已经无法自控\N{\ren}He's not himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.28,0:53:39.32,cn,,0,0,0,,还有 额 他不 他不会说话了 额\N{\ren}and, um, he can't, he can't talk, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.46,0:53:41.43,cn,,0,0,0,,对 额 他不会说话了\N{\ren}Yeah, uh, he doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.56,0:53:43.81,cn,,0,0,0,,他好像并不知道他生病了 但是\N{\ren}he doesn't seem to know he's sick, but, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.94,0:53:46.60,cn,,0,0,0,,如果有人能听到 请来帮忙啊\N{\ren}i-if someone can hear what I'm saying, please help.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.85,0:53:49.05,cn,,0,0,0,,额 喂\N{\ren}Uh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.19,0:53:52.71,cn,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\ren}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.09,0:53:56.96,cn,,0,0,0,,他妈的\N{\ren}Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.28,0:54:48.84,cn,,0,0,0,,我好担心你\N{\ren}I'm so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.05,0:54:56.19,cn,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办\N{\ren}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.20,0:55:09.00,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐\N{\ren}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.13,0:55:10.24,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐 快\N{\ren}Oh, my God. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.38,0:55:12.07,cn,,0,0,0,,我们上楼\N{\ren}Let's get you upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.21,0:55:13.52,cn,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\ren}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.02,0:56:07.19,cn,,0,0,0,,给 你能 额\N{\ren}Here. Can you, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.33,0:56:09.02,cn,,0,0,0,,你能写下来吗\N{\ren}Can you write it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.16,0:56:11.44,cn,,0,0,0,,告诉我出什么事了\N{\ren}Just tell me what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.22,0:56:40.47,cn,,0,0,0,,不\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.47,0:56:46.26,cn,,0,0,0,,你病了 仅此而已 但我们会治好你的\N{\ren}You're sick-- that's all-- but we're gonna fix you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.55,0:56:54.96,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克\N{\ren}Blake...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.41,0:57:00.93,cn,,0,0,0,,你会好起来的 因为咱宝贝儿需要你\N{\ren}You're gonna get better, because Ginger needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.07,0:57:03.49,cn,,0,0,0,,我需要你\N{\ren}I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.63,0:57:06.11,cn,,0,0,0,,没有你我办不到的\N{\ren}I can't do this without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.22,0:57:09.60,cn,,0,0,0,,我真正想说的是\N{\ren}What I-I really want to say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.29,0:57:13.88,cn,,0,0,0,,是\N{\ren}...is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.02,0:57:16.67,cn,,0,0,0,,我爱你 布莱克\N{\ren}is that I love you, Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.85,0:57:22.96,cn,,0,0,0,,没有你 我这辈子什么也不想做了\N{\ren}I don't want to do anything in my life without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.96,0:57:27.13,cn,,0,0,0,,你是我最好的朋友\N{\ren}You're my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.14,0:57:31.41,cn,,0,0,0,,我太爱你了\N{\ren}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.61,0:57:54.71,cn,,0,0,0,,夏 夏洛特\N{\ren}Ch-Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.30,0:57:59.44,cn,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\ren}What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.03,0:58:03.79,cn,,0,0,0,,我听不明白你说话\N{\ren}I can't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.69,0:58:10.49,cn,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊\N{\ren}What... what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.26,0:58:27.02,cn,,0,0,0,,他怎么了\N{\ren}What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.54,0:58:31.89,cn,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\ren}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.03,0:58:33.96,cn,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\ren}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.10,0:58:36.00,cn,,0,0,0,,过来吧\N{\ren}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.14,0:58:43.24,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸不太舒服 等到早上\N{\ren}Daddy's not feeling well, but in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.38,0:58:47.70,cn,,0,0,0,,我们就马上带他去看医生 好吗\N{\ren}we're gonna take him to the doctor as soon as we can, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.70,0:58:54.05,cn,,0,0,0,,你生病了吗 爸爸\N{\ren}Are you sick, Dada?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.20,0:59:05.85,cn,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\ren}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.99,0:59:08.03,cn,,0,0,0,,你怎么一直在流血\N{\ren}Why are you bleeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.17,0:59:10.24,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸的胳膊为什么会这样\N{\ren}Why is Daddy's arm like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.37,0:59:12.79,cn,,0,0,0,,-宝贝儿 额 -帮帮他啊 妈咪\N{\ren}-Ginger, um... -Help him, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.93,0:59:15.55,cn,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿 你去隔壁房间好吗\N{\ren}Baby, go to the next room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.73,0:59:23.94,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐\N{\ren}CHARLOTTE : Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.51,1:00:52.65,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱克\N{\ren}Blake.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.37,1:01:23.20,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.56,1:02:14.21,cn,,0,0,0,,好了 快点 快点\N{\ren}Okay, come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.35,1:02:16.97,cn,,0,0,0,,出来 出来吧 没事的\N{\ren}Out. Just come out. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.11,1:02:20.12,cn,,0,0,0,,没事的 没事\N{\ren}It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.78,1:02:30.44,cn,,0,0,0,,这边走 亲爱的\N{\ren}This way, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.44,1:02:33.68,cn,,0,0,0,,好的 来吧 来\N{\ren}Okay, come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.53,1:02:53.84,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪 要是他\N{\ren}Mommy, what if he...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.91,1:04:41.36,cn,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\N{\ren}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.88,1:04:44.88,cn,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\ren}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.57,1:04:50.16,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐\N{\ren}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.46,1:05:12.74,cn,,0,0,0,,好的 好的\N{\ren}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.87,1:05:14.53,cn,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.00,1:05:34.93,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪 他来了\N{\ren}Mommy, he's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.07,1:05:36.35,cn,,0,0,0,,上去\N{\ren}Up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.48,1:05:37.76,cn,,0,0,0,,快 爬上去\N{\ren}Quick. Climb up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.23,1:05:57.09,cn,,0,0,0,,别动\N{\ren}Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.35,1:06:51.35,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.49,1:06:53.32,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪 我要掉下去了\N{\ren}Mommy, please, I'm gonna fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.69,1:07:50.62,cn,,0,0,0,,快\N{\ren}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.02,1:08:19.02,cn,,0,0,0,,-你丢下了他 -什么\N{\ren}-You left him. -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.16,1:08:20.99,cn,,0,0,0,,你把爸爸留在外面 他会受伤的\N{\ren}You left Daddy outside. He's gonna get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.13,1:08:22.93,cn,,0,0,0,,-他会死掉的 你把他丢在外面等死 -不 不\N{\ren}-He's gonna die! You just left him outside to die! -No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.06,1:08:25.14,cn,,0,0,0,,不 他是在保护你\N{\ren}No, he was trying to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.21,1:08:32.49,cn,,0,0,0,,待在这儿\N{\ren}Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.53,1:08:44.67,cn,,0,0,0,,是爸爸吗\N{\ren}Is it Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.95,1:08:48.54,cn,,0,0,0,,他生病了\N{\ren}He's sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.68,1:08:50.26,cn,,0,0,0,,他需要我们\N{\ren}He needs us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.33,1:08:53.16,cn,,0,0,0,,开门啊 妈咪\N{\ren}Open the door, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.23,1:09:58.23,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\ren}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.81,1:10:29.23,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\ren}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.40,1:10:32.54,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\ren}Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.68,1:10:36.72,cn,,0,0,0,,我现在在想什么\N{\ren}what am I thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.75,1:10:39.51,cn,,0,0,0,,我在想什么\N{\ren}What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.24,1:10:45.07,cn,,0,0,0,,我在想我爱你\N{\ren}I was thinking that I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.39,1:10:53.97,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\ren}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.11,1:10:56.80,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸 你能听到我说话吗\N{\ren}Dad? Dad, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.50,1:11:01.91,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸 你没事吧\N{\ren}Daddy? Daddy, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.98,1:11:06.26,cn,,0,0,0,,我太爱你了\N{\ren}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.52,1:11:25.14,cn,,0,0,0,,快点 快点 起来 起来啊\N{\ren}Come on. Come on. Get up. Get up. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.28,1:11:26.83,cn,,0,0,0,,过来 过来\N{\ren}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.08,1:11:35.15,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\ren}Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.21,1:13:09.52,cn,,0,0,0,,进来 进来\N{\ren}Get in. Get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.87,1:13:12.73,cn,,0,0,0,,-进来 -妈咪\N{\ren}-Get in. -Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.73,1:13:44.42,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.84,1:14:57.53,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.96,1:17:03.31,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.65,1:17:06.69,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸为什么会生病啊\N{\ren}Why did Daddy have to get sick?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.87,1:17:10.49,cn,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\ren}Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.84,1:17:15.98,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸的父亲\N{\ren}Daddy's father...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.70,1:17:21.33,cn,,0,0,0,,不久前 他出去了 去了森林\N{\ren}A while ago, he went out... into the forest,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.46,1:17:23.92,cn,,0,0,0,,就再也没有回来\N{\ren}and he never came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.05,1:17:28.30,cn,,0,0,0,,所有人都以为他死了 可是\N{\ren}Everybody thought he was dead, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.44,1:17:30.92,cn,,0,0,0,,我想他只是病了\N{\ren}I think he just got sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.13,1:17:34.13,cn,,0,0,0,,跟爸爸一样的病吗\N{\ren}Sick like Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.65,1:17:37.03,cn,,0,0,0,,对\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.17,1:17:39.38,cn,,0,0,0,,我想他可能\N{\ren}I think he may have...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.52,1:17:42.07,cn,,0,0,0,,把这病传染给了爸爸\N{\ren}given his sickness to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.21,1:17:44.66,cn,,0,0,0,,我希望他回到原来的样子\N{\ren}I want him back the way he was.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.66,1:17:49.73,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道 我也是 亲爱的\N{\ren}I know. Me, too, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.87,1:17:51.84,cn,,0,0,0,,我 我也希望他变回去\N{\ren}I-I want him back, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.81,1:18:00.26,cn,,0,0,0,,我会一直陪着你的\N{\ren}I'm always going to be here for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.72,1:18:13.83,cn,,0,0,0,,不 妈咪\N{\ren}No. Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.86,1:18:16.69,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.05,1:19:43.16,cn,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\ren}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.03,1:20:25.75,cn,,0,0,0,,退后 退后 退后\N{\ren}Get back! Get back! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.20,1:20:30.00,cn,,0,0,0,,求你了 爸爸 你吓到我了\N{\ren}Please, Daddy, you're scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.14,1:20:31.97,cn,,0,0,0,,不\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.35,1:20:35.87,cn,,0,0,0,,不不\N{\ren}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.00,1:20:37.73,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.12,1:20:46.50,cn,,0,0,0,,这儿 来\N{\ren}In here. Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.70,1:23:37.43,cn,,0,0,0,,来啊 来\N{\ren}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.64,1:26:02.05,cn,,0,0,0,,快 妈咪 他来了\N{\ren}Hurry, Mommy. He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.19,1:26:03.19,cn,,0,0,0,,给 拿着这个\N{\ren}Here. Just hold this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.33,1:26:04.99,cn,,0,0,0,,拿好\N{\ren}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.66,1:26:20.31,cn,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\N{\ren}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.04,1:26:28.67,cn,,0,0,0,,没关系 来啊 来\N{\ren}All right. All right. Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.72,1:28:32.62,cn,,0,0,0,,妈咪\N{\ren}Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.28,1:28:39.35,cn,,0,0,0,,他希望这一切都结束\N{\ren}He wants this to be over.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.95,1:30:04.43,cn,,0,0,0,,哦 布莱克\N{\ren}Oh, Blake.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.20,1:30:19.93,cn,,0,0,0,,有我在 有我在\N{\ren}I'm here. I'm here.
